was $17.3 billion, up $0.1 billion from the prior year. the adjustment for net
gains on asset sales was $3.2 billion compared to an adjustment of $1.8 billion
in 2013. changes in operational working capital, excluding cash and debt,
decreased cash in 2014 by $4.9 billion.
